{
  "stem": "24268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My brother was-- like I said, my parents always to put the priority to send to the best school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was going to one of-- private school, one of the highest rated schools in the country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was the [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Yavna ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Fistenburg. ?] And after that, he will attend to engineering school, or [SPEAKING POLISH], in Katowice, which there Jews were not permitted to attend.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But as a non-Jew-- we had a client which she was the director of the colleges.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she was in contact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So she tried to-- because I mean, we had a Polish name, Zarasinski, she told them, [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Josef ?] Zarasinski, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Joseph ?] Zarasinski.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's the way she called.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she-- that's the way he got into this college, engineering.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And natur-- and there was another Jew, also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But they did not know he was Jewish-- [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Lonav ?] Davinsky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were the only two which attended school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he got his diploma just before the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And naturally then, by the end, when they-- he got the diploma, they revealed-- that realized that he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But it was too late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They had to give him the diploma.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister's name was Frania.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was the most beautiful child-- intelligent, as young as she was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was like a tomboy-- beautiful green eyes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody loved her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in fact, and when I was in-- in 1989, we'd been visiting with my husband in Israel, the gathering for Sosnowiec, from our town.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to-- we wore our name on the blouse, or whatever we wear.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some lady approached me with her granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she looked at the name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She says, you know, she-- and I quote it she said to the granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
